Replacement method for cyto_names

Source: R/cyto-helpers.R
cyto_names-set.Rd

Replacement method for cyto_names

cyto_names(x) <- value

Arguments

x

object of class flowFrame, flowSet, GatingHierarchy or GatingSet.
value

vector of replacement names.

Examples


library(CytoExploreRData)

# Activation flowSet
fs <- Activation

# Sample names
cyto_names(fs)
#>  [1] "Activation_1.fcs"  "Activation_2.fcs"  "Activation_3.fcs" 
#>  [4] "Activation_4.fcs"  "Activation_5.fcs"  "Activation_6.fcs" 
#>  [7] "Activation_7.fcs"  "Activation_8.fcs"  "Activation_9.fcs" 
#> [10] "Activation_10.fcs" "Activation_11.fcs" "Activation_12.fcs"
#> [13] "Activation_13.fcs" "Activation_14.fcs" "Activation_15.fcs"
#> [16] "Activation_16.fcs" "Activation_17.fcs" "Activation_18.fcs"
#> [19] "Activation_19.fcs" "Activation_20.fcs" "Activation_21.fcs"
#> [22] "Activation_22.fcs" "Activation_23.fcs" "Activation_24.fcs"
#> [25] "Activation_25.fcs" "Activation_26.fcs" "Activation_27.fcs"
#> [28] "Activation_28.fcs" "Activation_29.fcs" "Activation_30.fcs"
#> [31] "Activation_31.fcs" "Activation_32.fcs" "Activation_33.fcs"

# Change first sample name
cyto_names(fs)[1] <- "first_sample"

# Activation GatingSet
gs <- GatingSet(fs)

# Change last sample name
cyto_names(gs)[length(gs)] <- "last_sample"

# Updated sample names
cyto_names(gs)
#>  [1] "first_sample"      "Activation_2.fcs"  "Activation_3.fcs" 
#>  [4] "Activation_4.fcs"  "Activation_5.fcs"  "Activation_6.fcs" 
#>  [7] "Activation_7.fcs"  "Activation_8.fcs"  "Activation_9.fcs" 
#> [10] "Activation_10.fcs" "Activation_11.fcs" "Activation_12.fcs"
#> [13] "Activation_13.fcs" "Activation_14.fcs" "Activation_15.fcs"
#> [16] "Activation_16.fcs" "Activation_17.fcs" "Activation_18.fcs"
#> [19] "Activation_19.fcs" "Activation_20.fcs" "Activation_21.fcs"
#> [22] "Activation_22.fcs" "Activation_23.fcs" "Activation_24.fcs"
#> [25] "Activation_25.fcs" "Activation_26.fcs" "Activation_27.fcs"
#> [28] "Activation_28.fcs" "Activation_29.fcs" "Activation_30.fcs"
#> [31] "Activation_31.fcs" "Activation_32.fcs" "last_sample"
